Name: Sentence Classification
Description: Contains sentences from the abstract and introduction of 30 articles annotated with a modified Argumentative Zones annotation scheme. These articles come from biology, machine learning and psychology.

Name: Sentiment Labelled Sentences
Description: The dataset contains sentences labelled with positive or negative sentiment.

Name: ser Knowledge Modeling Data (Students' Knowledge Levels on DC Electrical Machines)
Description: The dataset is about the users' learning activities and knowledge levels on subjects of DC Electrical Machines. The dataset had been obtained from online web-courses and reported in my Ph.D. Thesis.

Name: Servo
Description: Data was from a simulation of a servo system

Name: SGEMM GPU kernel performance
Description: Running times for multiplying two 2048 x 2048 matrices using a GPU OpenCL SGEMM kernel with varying parameters (using the library 'CLTune').

Name: Shoulder Implant X-Ray Manufacturer Classification
Description: 597 de-identified raw X-ray scans of implanted shoulder prostheses from four manufactures.

Name: Shuttle Landing Control
Description: Tiny database; all nominal values

Name: SIFT10M
Description: In SIFT10M, each data point is a SIFT feature which is extracted from Caltech-256 by the open source VLFeat library. The corresponding patches of the SIFT features are provided.

Name: Simulated Falls and Daily Living Activities Data Set
Description: 20 falls and 16 daily living activities were performed by 17 volunteers with 5 repetitions while wearing 6 sensors (3.060 instances) that attached to their head, chest, waist, wrist, thigh and ankle.

Name: SkillCraft1 Master Table Dataset
Description: This data was used in Thompson et al. (2013). A list of possible game actions is discussed in Thompson, Blair, Chen, & Henrey (2013).

Name: Skin Segmentation
Description: The Skin Segmentation dataset is constructed over B, G, R color space. Skin and Nonskin dataset is generated using skin textures from face images of diversity of age, gender, and race people.

Name: Smartphone Dataset for Human Activity Recognition (HAR) in Ambient Assisted Living (AAL)
Description: This data is an addition to an existing dataset on UCI. We collected more data to improve the accuracy of our human activity recognition algorithms applied in the domain of Ambient Assisted Living.

Name: Smartphone-Based Recognition of Human Activities and Postural Transitions
Description: Activity recognition data set built from the recordings of 30 subjects performing basic activities and postural transitions while carrying a waist-mounted smartphone with embedded inertial sensors.

Name: SML2010
Description: This dataset is collected from a monitor system mounted in a domotic house. It corresponds to approximately 40 days of monitoring data.

Name: SMS Spam Collection
Description: The SMS Spam Collection is a public set of SMS labeled messages that have been collected for mobile phone spam research.

Name: Solar Flare
Description: Each class attribute counts the number of solar flares of a certain class that occur in a 24 hour period

Name: Somerville Happiness Survey
Description: A data extract of a non-federal dataset posted here https

Name: South German Credit
Description: 700 good and 300 bad credits with 20 predictor variables. Data from 1973 to 1975. Stratified sample from actual credits with bad credits heavily oversampled. A cost matrix can be used.

Name: Soybean (Large)
Description: Michalski's famous soybean disease database

Name: Soybean (Small)
Description: Michalski's famous soybean disease database

Name: Spambase
Description: Classifying Email as Spam or Non-Spam

Name: Speaker Accent Recognition
Description: Data set featuring single English words read by speakers from six different countries for accent detection and recognition

Name: SPECT Heart
Description: Data on cardiac Single Proton Emission Computed Tomography (SPECT) images. Each patient classified into two categories

Name: SPECTF Heart
Description: Data on cardiac Single Proton Emission Computed Tomography (SPECT) images. Each patient classified into two categories

Name: Spoken Arabic Digit
Description: This dataset contains timeseries of mel-frequency cepstrum coefficients (MFCCs) corresponding to spoken Arabic digits. Includes data from 44 male and 44 female native Arabic speakers.

Name: Sponge
Description: Data on sponges; Attributes in spanish

Name: Sports articles for objectivity analysis
Description: 1000 sports articles were labeled using Amazon Mechanical Turk as objective or subjective. The raw texts, extracted features, and the URLs from which the articles were retrieved are provided.

Name: Statlog (Australian Credit Approval)
Description: This file concerns credit card applications. This database exists elsewhere in the repository (Credit Screening Database) in a slightly different form

Name: Statlog (German Credit Data)
Description: This dataset classifies people described by a set of attributes as good or bad credit risks. Comes in two formats (one all numeric). Also comes with a cost matrix

Name: Statlog (Heart)
Description: This dataset is a heart disease database similar to a database already present in the repository (Heart Disease databases) but in a slightly different form

Name: Statlog (Image Segmentation)
Description: This dataset is an image segmentation database similar to a database already present in the repository (Image segmentation database) but in a slightly different form.

Name: Statlog (Landsat Satellite)
Description: Multi-spectral values of pixels in 3x3 neighbourhoods in a satellite image, and the classification associated with the central pixel in each neighbourhood

Name: Statlog (Shuttle)
Description: The shuttle dataset contains 9 attributes all of which are numerical. Approximately 80% of the data belongs to class 1

Name: Statlog (Vehicle Silhouettes)
Description: 3D objects within a 2D image by application of an ensemble of shape feature extractors to the 2D silhouettes of the objects.

Name: Statlog Project
Description: Various Databases

Name: Steel Plates Faults
Description: A dataset of steel plates’ faults, classified into 7 different types. The goal was to train machine learning for automatic pattern recognition.

Name: Stock portfolio performance
Description: The data set of performances of weighted scoring stock portfolios are obtained with mixture design from the US stock market historical database.

Name: StoneFlakes
Description: Stone flakes are waste products of the stone tool production in the prehistoric era. The variables are means of geometric and stylistic features of the flakes contained in different inventories.

Name: Student Academics Performance
Description: The dataset tried to find the end semester percentage prediction based on different social, economic and academic attributes.

Name: Student Loan Relational
Description: Student Loan Relational Domain

Name: Student Performance
Description: Predict student performance in secondary education (high school).

Name: Superconductivty Data
Description: Two file s contain data on 21263 superconductors and their relevant features.

Name: SUSY
Description: This is a classification problem to distinguish between a signal process which produces supersymmetric particles and a background process which does not.

Name: Swarm Behaviour
Description: This dataset achieved from an online survey, which is run by UNSW, Australia. It contains three data of ' Flocking - Not Flocking', 'Aligned - Not Aligned', and 'Grouped - Not Grouped'.

Name: Synthetic Control Chart Time Series
Description: This data consists of synthetically generated control charts.

Name: Syskill and Webert Web Page Ratings
Description: This database contains HTML source of web pages plus the ratings of a single user on these web pages. Web pages are on four seperate subjects (Bands- recording artists; Goats; Sheep; and BioMedical)

Name: Tamilnadu Electricity Board Hourly Readings
Description: This data can be effectively produced the result to fewer parameter of the Load profile can be reduced in the Database

Name: Tarvel Review Ratings
Description: Google reviews on attractions from 24 categories across Europe are considered. Google user rating ranges from 1 to 5 and average user rating per category is calculated.

Name: Taxi Service Trajectory - Prediction Challenge, ECML PKDD 2015
Description: An accurate dataset describing trajectories performed by all the 442 taxis running in the city of Porto, in Portugal.

Name: Teaching Assistant Evaluation
Description: The data consist of evaluations of teaching performance; scores are "low", "medium", or "high"

Name: Tennis Major Tournament Match Statistics
Description: This is a collection of 8 files containing the match statistics for both women and men at the four major tennis tournaments of the year 2013. Each file has 42 columns and a minimum of 76 rows.

Name: Thoracic Surgery Data
Description: The data is dedicated to classification problem related to the post-operative life expectancy in the lung cancer patients

Name: Thyroid Disease
Description: 10 separate databases from Garavan Institute

Name: Tic-Tac-Toe Endgame
Description: Binary classification task on possible configurations of tic-tac-toe game

Name: Trains
Description: 2 data formats (structured, one-instance-per-line)

Name: Travel Reviews
Description: Reviews on destinations in 10 categories mentioned across East Asia. Each traveler rating is mapped as Excellent(4), Very Good(3), Average(2), Poor(1), and Terrible(0) and average rating is used.

Name: TTC-3600: Benchmark dataset for Turkish text categorization
Description: The TTC-3600 data set is a collection of Turkish news and articles including categorized 3,600 documents from 6 well-known portals in Turkey. It has 4 different forms in ARFF Weka format.

Name: Turkiye Student Evaluation
Description: This data set contains a total 5820 evaluation scores provided by students from Gazi University in Ankara (Turkey). There is a total of 28 course specific questions and additional 5 attributes.

Name: TV News Channel Commercial Detection Dataset
Description: TV Commercials data set consists of standard audio-visual features of video shots extracted from 150 hours of TV news broadcast of 3 Indian and 2 international news channels ( 30 Hours each).

Name: Twenty Newsgroups
Description: This data set consists of 20000 messages taken from 20 newsgroups.

Name: Twin gas sensor arrays
Description: 5 replicates of an 8-MOX gas sensor array were exposed to different gas conditions (4 volatiles at 10 concentration levels each).

Name: Twitter Data set for Arabic Sentiment Analysis
Description: This problem of Sentiment Analysis (SA) has been studied well on the English language but not Arabic one. Two main approaches have been devised

Name: UbiqLog (smartphone lifelogging)
Description: UbiqLog is the smartphone lifelogging tool that runs on the smartphone of 35 users for about 2 months.

Name: UJI Pen Characters
Description: Data consists of written characters in a UNIPEN-like format

Name: UJI Pen Characters (Version 2)
Description: A pen-based database with more than 11k isolated handwritten characters

Name: UJIIndoorLoc
Description: The UJIIndoorLoc is a Multi-Building Multi-Floor indoor localization database to test Indoor Positioning System that rely on WLAN/WiFi fingerprint.

Name: UJIIndoorLoc-Mag
Description: The UJIIndoorLoc-Mag is an indoor localization database to test Indoor Positioning System that rely on Earth's magnetic field variations.

Name: Ultrasonic flowmeter diagnostics
Description: Fault diagnosis of four liquid ultrasonic flowmeters

Name: Undocumented
Description: Various datasets without documentation (feel free to explore!)

Name: University
Description: Data in original (LISP-readable) form

Name: University of Tehran Question Dataset 2016 (UTQD.2016)
Description: Persian questions gathered from a jeopardy game broadcasted on Iranian national television.

Name: UNIX User Data
Description: This file contains 9 sets of sanitized user data drawn from the command histories of 8 UNIX computer users at Purdue over the course of up to 2 years.

Name: Urban Land Cover
Description: Classification of urban land cover using high resolution aerial imagery. Intended to assist sustainable urban planning efforts.

Name: URL Reputation
Description: Anonymized 120-day subset of the ICML-09 URL data containing 2.4 million examples and 3.2 million features.

Name: US Census Data (1990)
Description: The USCensus1990raw data set contains a one percent sample of the Public Use Microdata Samples (PUMS) person records drawn from the full 1990 census sample.

Name: User Identification From Walking Activity
Description: The dataset collects data from an Android smartphone positioned in the chest pocket from 22 participants walking in the wild over a predefined path.

Name: User Knowledge Modeling
Description: It is the real dataset about the students' knowledge status about the subject of Electrical DC Machines. The dataset had been obtained from Ph.D. Thesis.

Name: USPTO Algorithm Challenge, run by NASA-Harvard Tournament Lab and TopCoder    Problem: Pat
Description: Data used for USPTO Algorithm Competition. Contains drawing pages from US patents with manually labeled figure and part labels.

Name: Vertebral Column
Description: Data set containing values for six biomechanical features used to classify orthopaedic patients into 3 classes (normal, disk hernia or spondilolysthesis) or 2 classes (normal or abnormal).

Name: Vicon Physical Action Data Set
Description: The Physical Action Data Set includes 10 normal and 10 aggressive physical actions that measure the human activity. The data have been collected by 10 subjects using the Vicon 3D tracker.

Name: Victorian Era Authorship Attribution
Description: To create the largest authorship attribution dataset, we extracted works of 50 well-known authors. To have a non-exhaustive learning, in training there are 45 authors whereas, in the testing, it's 50

Name: Volcanoes on Venus - JARtool experiment
Description: The JARtool project was a pioneering effort to develop an automatic system for cataloging small volcanoes in the large set of Venus images returned by the Magellan spacecraft.

Name: Wall-Following Robot Navigation Data

Name: Water Treatment Plant
Description: Multiple classes predict plant state

Name: Wave Energy Converters
Description: This data set consists of positions and absorbed power outputs of wave energy converters (WECs) in four real wave scenarios from the southern coast of Australia.

Name: Waveform Database Generator (Version 1)
Description: CART book's waveform domains

Name: Waveform Database Generator (Version 2)
Description: CART book's waveform domains

Name: Wearable Computing: Classification of Body Postures and Movements (PUC-Rio)
Description: A dataset with 5 classes (sitting-down, standing-up, standing, walking, and sitting) collected on 8 hours of activities of 4 healthy subjects. We also established a baseline performance index.

Name: Website Phishing
Description: This dataset collected mainly from: PhishTank archive, MillerSmiles archive, Google’s searching operators.

Name: Weight Lifting Exercises monitored with Inertial Measurement Units
Description: Six young health subjects were asked to perform 5 variations of the biceps curl weight lifting exercise. One of the variations is the one predicted by the health professional.

Name: WESAD (Wearable Stress and Affect Detection)
Description: WESAD (Wearable Stress and Affect Detection) contains data of 15 subjects during a stress-affect lab study, while wearing physiological and motion sensors.

Name: Wholesale customers
Description: The data set refers to clients of a wholesale distributor. It includes the annual spending in monetary units (m.u.) on diverse product categories

Name: wiki4HE
Description: Survey of faculty members from two Spanish universities on teaching uses of Wikipedia

Name: Wilt
Description: High-resolution Remote Sensing data set (Quickbird). Small number of training samples of diseased trees, large number for other land cover. Testing data set from stratified random sample of image.

Name: Wine
Description: Using chemical analysis determine the origin of wines

Name: Wine Quality
Description: Two datasets are included, related to red and white vinho verde wine samples, from the north of Portugal. The goal is to model wine quality based on physicochemical tests (see [Cortez et al., 2009], http

Name: Wireless Indoor Localization
Description: Collected in indoor space by observing signal strengths of seven WiFi signals visible on a smartphone. The decision variable is one of the four rooms.

Name: WISDM Smartphone and Smartwatch Activity and Biometrics Dataset

Name: YearPredictionMSD

Name: Yeast
Description: Predicting the Cellular Localization Sites of Proteins

Name: YouTube Multiview Video Games Dataset
Description: This dataset contains about 120k instances, each described by 13 feature types, with class information, specially useful for exploring multiview topics (cotraining, ensembles, clustering,..).

Name: YouTube Spam Collection
Description: It is a public set of comments collected for spam research. It has five datasets composed by 1,956 real messages extracted from five videos that were among the 10 most viewed on the collection period.

Name: Z-Alizadeh Sani
Description: It was collected for CAD diagnosis.

Name: Zoo
Description: Artificial, 7 classes of animals
